quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  3,10,"Pellet …ďen yeddu…ďe Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, jawle ma…ď…ďe e …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe ha…óataa …ďe lepte Alla …óen aduna e laakara. ∆Āen siforii…ďe …óin sifaaji, ko hu…ď…ďiniroytee…ďe jahannama …ďen √Īalnde darngal."
  3,11,"∆Āee yeddu…ďe hino wa'i wa yim…ďe Fir'awna e adinoo…ďe …ďe immorde e yeddunoo…ďe Alla …ďe fenni aayeeje Makko, O Leptiri …ďe sabu junubaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin, jawle e …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe nafaano …ďe. Alla ko Sa…ótude leptugol …ďen yeddoo…ďe Mo, fenna aaYeeje Makko."
  3,12,"Maakan …ďen yeddu…ďe (an Nulaa…óo) no …ďe …óuu…óiri diinaaji: "ar-ma ka muumini en foolata on, maaydon e keeferaaku, Alla Moo…ďitoya on ka yiite jahannama". Nge bonii nda…ó…óudi mon."
  3,13,"Gom…óii laatanike on dalil e tasakuyee e …óin feddeeji …ói…ói fottudi fii ha…ďugol √Īalnde "badri": fedde goo ko gom…óinde; ko nden woni fedde Nulaa…óo Alla on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun e sahaaba en makko, hi…ďe ha…ďira e laawol Alla fii no Konngol Alla ngol …ďamtora dow, konngol yeddu…ďe …ďen jippora ley. Ndeya fedde ko yeddunde; ko …ďen woni heefer…ďe makka …ďen yaltunoo…ďe no yiinoo maŇčtoo, muumini en hino yi'ira …ďen gii…óe gite, jaasu…ďe yeeso ma…ď…ďe ka haqiiqa. Alla Wallitii yi…ó…ďe Makko …ďen, Alla no no Semmbinira ballal Makko ngal On Mo O Muuyi. No e koo ko jaŇčtaa …óoo, waaju wonannde joomiraa…ďe-haqqillaaji, fii yo …ďe anndu wonde ballal ngal ko fii muumini en; hay si …ďe …óuu…óaa e limoore, e wonde fooleede nden ko fii yim…ďe mehre …ďen; hay si …ďe …óuu…óii e limoore."
  3,14,"Allaahu Toowu…óo On Hino Humpita wonde O Cu…óinanii yim…ďe …ďen ka jarribagol …ďe, yi…óugol tuuyooji aduna: wano rew…ďe, e …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe, e jawle heewu…óe tugindiraa…óe, immorde e kaŇčŇče e kaalise, e remugol ka leydi; …óum non ko dakamme nguurndam aduna, hino dakmitoree dumunna refti muta. Haanaa nde gom…óim…óo humondirta e …óum, Alla, ko ka Makko KaŇčko tun ruttorde mo∆ī∆īunde woodi; ko nden woni Aljanna on mo yaajeendi mun fota kammu e leydi."
  3,15,"Maaku an Muhammadu: "E yo mi humpitu on ko …ďuri …óin tuuyooji mo∆ī∆īude?". Hino woodani …ďen hulu…ďe Alla, …ďe …óoftii Mo, …ďe ha…óitii yeddugol Mo, Aljannaaji: hino ila senngo ley ku…ďeeje e le…ó…óe majji, can…ói; ko …ďe luttiŇčtee…ďe ton, ko aldaa e maayde maa mulugol, hino woodani ton rew…ďe la…ď…ďinaa…ďe jikku e tagudi e kala bone, hino woodani …ďe kadi yarluyee Alla on jippotoo…óo e ma…ď…ďe, O TikkaŇčtaa…ďe poomaa. Alla ko ReŇčtu…óo fiyakuuji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, hunnde e majji suu…óaaki, O Yo…ďitiroyay…ďe …óum."